,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T06:02:47.000Z","msg":"8日假 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都未有得放<br />\n留明 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63b74eba07ef2e4b739fd4547805559929fb1368","tid":451313,"uid":13919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T06:05:10.000Z","msg":"小豆島好撚麻煩，船班次都算，到左島上之後搭車火都黎<br />\n勸你咁即興冇plan過就唔好去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一係plan左先"},{"pid":"d90862bf5461ce9b1b23b29c99adc47152504a4a","tid":451313,"uid":16654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T06:06:50.000Z","msg":"第一次嘗試用文字記錄旅行<br />\n希望用盡我腦汁修飾得好d<br />\n<br />\n今晚七點左右會到高松，到時再寫<br />\n多謝各位"},{"pid":"fb8e63ae175e05f125c7642200a01b56133ac203","tid":451313,"uid":16654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T06:07:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小豆島好撚麻煩，船班次都算，到左島上之後搭車火都黎<br />\n勸你咁即興冇plan過就唔好去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一係plan左先</blockquote><br />\n好"},{"pid":"0ecd5b38a43f4b3f2e00f2b2c3d0936b38500c42","tid":451313,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T06:12:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 等update"},{"pid":"52ba62e270310be8f36581aaa0f51c0d47e8f18e","tid":451313,"uid":16654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T11:02:35.000Z","msg":"啱啱落機，呢家坐車去高松站<br />\n機上面magic hour 真係次次睇都咁靚<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/29/190222_31aee4e184fe7e78e897f69e91c407ae.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F29%2F190222_31aee4e184fe7e78e897f69e91c407ae.jpg&h=495d5ac1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n頭先發現高松機場係冇7仔<br />\n連日yen都冇唱嘅我<br />\n嘗試用atm㩒錢，點知下下都exceed withdraw limit<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/29/190029_130e01638771d39d20b