itedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T14:07:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>錢又冇, 住宿又未搵, 連聽日去邊都唔知<br />\n<br />\n一係你就好熟四國, 熟到簡單睇一睇就知點搭車, 咁就型<br />\n如果唔係, 你只會每日徘徊等車/走車/等車/走車</blockquote><br />\n完全唔熟四國<br />\n聽日打算去德島stay 一晚<br />\n上面有巴打話小豆島唔熟路會有麻煩<br />\n而且我諗搭船都要現金<br />\n好彩係uo上面買咗jr pass 5日<br />\n搭去德島好似係最好選擇<br />\n<br />\n而家睇定路線同時間表先"},{"pid":"444e1d0b97a13d480da76f637e773c52fb6656c7","tid":451313,"uid":44377,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T14:12:45.000Z","msg":"即興四國真係有d難，無咩詳細planning最後會花好多時間係等車到，你最好都係認真計劃一下先，唔想見到你日日花幾粒鐘轉車等車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9fc4628a69c84e20188c08d3b3c8cb5ed655867","tid":451313,"uid":67028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T14:18:19.000Z","msg":"四國D野好散 你咁去<br />\n一日可能真係睇得一樣野"},{"pid":"3498d0fd4e8ab93067827d0e2011ef19de590b5a","tid":451313,"uid":2914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T14:20:42.000Z","msg":"遲D都想去高松<br />\n玩5日夠唔夠或者有冇咁多野玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31d149aa6c5960003b15a18ba67547885f29f34b","tid":451313,"uid":19310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T14:34:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>四國D野好散 你咁去<br />\n一日可能真係睇得一樣野</blockquote><br />\n我估佢一日一樣都難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf7fee4e776abd31378bf9b5fbbbf3d06f1ab46c","tid":451313,"uid":5241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T20:53:48.000Z","msg":"好想去多次四國<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5397e74e38e12691c749428db9b44341d4ea3d7","tid":451313,"uid":16654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T22:32:08.000Z","msg":"早晨咁多位<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/30/063100_9e6d105ae9cf5361a6cca54ff3fccedc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"htt