r />\n唔洗瞓街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n10000yen 邊度黎？</blockquote><br />\n碌卡掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac2e4071c0f18294c61a9d5f501092a4545afb38","tid":451313,"uid":16654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T10:54:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>揾到今晚stay嘅温泉酒店<br />\n連早晚 10000 yen<br />\n<br />\n唔洗瞓街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n10000yen 邊度黎？</blockquote><br />\n信用卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cd2b5b0fb01987d68e4096d1a97aabe94f4aff8","tid":451313,"uid":16654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T11:12:02.000Z","msg":"今日去左天使之路，同風車就返咗酒店放低野<br />\n每個位都逗留咗大概一到兩個鐘<br />\n天使之路去錯時間，冇其他人睇咁靚<br />\n上去瞭望台有隻貓勁他條係到望海景<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n風車同欖園都幾舒服，好多人扮魔女飛<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小豆島d 車都幾梳同幾亂<br />\n太早天黑就唔到時間去廿四瞳<br />\n希望聽日去埋其他地方<br />\n<br />\n返到酒店係四點幾，太陽開始落山<br />\n沿住岸邊慢慢行睇日落<br />\n住嘅地方附近有好多豉油廠，一路行都有陣日本豉油味<br />\n見到有個小朋友同佢老豆對住夕陽釣魚<br />\n成個感覺好溫馨好浪漫<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連登今日下晝開始up唔到圖<br />\n後補"},{"pid":"ae39d4fab144138df5bf5829bc89b1afa435f6c1","tid":451313,"uid":55,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T11:23:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6cdf844c5b83e30436f27174d46e4c895fe76afa","tid":451313,"uid":12994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T15:17:34.000Z","msg":"你有無銀聯？<br />\nVisa 好似禁唔到"},{"pid":"a41f72b42384b2cc33fc49acebd4db88eda21615","tid":451313,"uid":62815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T15:30:48.000Z","msg":"唔plan就咁德島高知高松玩下都得嘅<br />\n去埋金刀/栗林都差不多"},{"pid":"eb25376fcc453a0d39b9089f5450d142b40b2d76","tid":451313,"uid":12908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T15:33:20.000Z","msg":"去小豆島踩單車啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ae642330001ae78694dc976b4d0c5b497fb069a","tid":451313,"uid":64345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T10:38:45.000Z","msg":"今日樓主去咗邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d56fe7df9c56a01530f6fa050a8583e05fce5e72","tid":451313,"uid":808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T11:10:08.000Z","msg":"如果唔plan，好難去到蔓橋果邊，一日得3，4班車。"},{"pid":"e1598f81990d0c41d12a6dceffcf4a0bfa52da4e","tid":451313,"uid":23107,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T11:16:28.000Z","msg":"岩岩起四国翻嚟，有無咩幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7985b55c3041673ffbd3028f3a0e993b2cf17c68","tid":451313,"uid":16654,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T13:12:42.000Z","msg":"今日朝早checkout之後去返天使之道<br />\n今次有d若隱若現，唔錯<br />\n全日天晴，甚至係曬<br />\n上瞭望台望下，又見到琴日個隻貓係到曬太陽<br />\n唔通佢係個到嘅守護神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n欣賞完隻貓一輪之後，死火<br />\n行去土庄港要26分鐘，但係我下班船係20分鐘之後開，miss咗嘅話又要等多一個鐘<br />\n出盡奶力起勢咁跑，但係揹住成10kg backpack 真係好辛苦(平時唔做多d運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n跑到最後500米仲有3分鐘<br />\n好彩有個呀姨揸緊車見我跑到狗咁請我搭順風車(人間溫暖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n趕到船返高松啦"},{"pid":"25eb191673d6b2e4e97cb70927b867493aa21583","tid":451313,"uid":16654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T13:41:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>岩岩起四国翻嚟，有無咩幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有冇邊d地方有突發事件，要小心or注意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67b99c838a5c4a349b9844d3d75f764bda71e948","tid":45