彩有個呀姨揸緊車見我跑到狗咁請我搭順風車(人間溫暖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n趕到船返高松啦</blockquote><br />\n結果今日就係返兜天使之道？</blockquote><br />\n今日仲去左屋島同德島，呢家打"},{"pid":"cc249e4359da236c5988f2357b703fe10f4bc231","tid":451313,"uid":16654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T14:43:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名睇字先<br />\n個app冇幅圖睇到</blockquote><br />\n我琴日開始up唔到圖，等陣試下"},{"pid":"4eb47c3f1df0c1526412023f640d7b9b5591e5d8","tid":451313,"uid":23107,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T16:50:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>岩岩起四国翻嚟，有無咩幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有冇邊d地方有突發事件，要小心or注意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n回程翻香港個日要plan定 Jr高松駅去空港架巴士有時刻表<br />\n如果無估錯你應該撘1330 班機 咁你就要1019上巴士 因為之後個班已經係12xx<br />\n你可以去下松山 好玩過高松 如果你想問香川or愛媛縣既野可以問我 我都答到你<br />\n最後想講一樣野 時刻表真係好重要 尤其是你去四国<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79cd83db2dc40838ca32e3787ccebd9b60e8554b","tid":451313,"uid":16654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T00:26:59.000Z","msg":"返左高松之後就試左租單車<br />\n一日先100 yen 好抵<br />\n因為大部份都平路關係就算冇波都踩得好舒服<br />\n踩左去屋島站係附近又因為撚貓miss 左班上山嘅巴士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上到去之後有神社同寺廟<br />\n參觀左一陣就行去其中一個觀景台 (獅子觀景台 好似係)<br />\n係上面望返落黎真係好正<br />\n係超廣闊城市景，右面係男木島，女木島<br />\n左面係高松市全貌同高松港<br />\n量角器都唔洗度，應該有160 度<br />\n係一個大晴天有咁嘅景，唯一一點可惜嘅係<br />\n有好大個太陽呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n莫講話相機，眼都打唔開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以奉勸各位唔好下晝先上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/01/082626_fbf082e533b7ecd4607e67b1fec57f3e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F01%2F082626_fbf082e533b7ecd4607e67b1fec57f3e.jpg&h=763854af&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/01/082648_f45555724549a78d1f4e3189b9ac49a0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F01%2F082648_f45555724549a78d1f4e3189b9ac49a0.jpg&h=c907f2e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n落咗黎之後做左個好錯嘅決定，令到今日嘅我被迫放棄睇螺旋丸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6abd6906bd949b4775e4f65882318ec01ec17662","tid":451313,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T00:57:57.000Z","msg":"lm"}]}